    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the FEA model ensemble has achieved sufficient credibility for the intended COU. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; 12 of 13 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs required 3) is noted but deemed acceptable by the team given the strong quantitative agreement observed across all three QoIs and the conservative nature of the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol. Assurance level declared High based on overall factor performance and quantitative validation metrics. Model risk level 3 with Medium decision consequence and Medium model influence supports this determination.",
